# peaclock — tracked by chezmoi. COLOURS ONLY; peaclock's default view, size
# and layout are left untouched.
#
# Named 4-bit ANSI colours (not hex) resolve through the TERMINAL's themed
# palette, so the clock follows the active theme LIVE — no restart. In the
# theme-system's Ghostty palette, green (slot 2) and magenta (slot 5) both map to
# the Material primary in light and dark, so the clock tracks the primary accent
# automatically when the wallpaper/theme changes.

style text green
style active-fg green
style colon-fg green
